If you're looking for more laughs, then please check out our Facebook,

137
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:05,839
Twitter, Instagram and YouTube pages.

138
00:06:05,839 --> 00:06:08,839
You may find something to make you chuckle or guffaw there.

139
